// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/McXcDr oriented disc, 2024 by jt
// see also https://www.shadertoy.com/view/MffcWr oriented ring

// Exact euclidean distance to an oriented (i.e. perpendicular to given normal vector) disc.

// tags: sdf, distance, disc, euclidean, exact, oriented

